ridge Industries]] |date=September 7, 2018 |accessdate=May 10, 2019 |archiveurl=http://www.webcitation.org/78G0IGv5k |archivedate=May 9, 2018 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"THR Cast\">{{cite web |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/red-dead-redemption-2-cast-interview-how-new-western-was-made-1157998 |title=How 'Red Dead Redemption 2's' Stars Brought a New Western Classic to Life |last=Shanley |first=Patrick |work=[[The Hollywood Reporter]] |publisher=[[Eldridge Industries]] |date=November 8, 2018 |accessdate=May 14, 2019 |archiveurl=http://www.webcitation.org/78KXasAPQ |archivedate=May 12, 2018 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Twinfinite Clark\">{{cite web |url=https://twinfinite.net/2019/02/red-dead-redemption-2-interview-arthurs-voice-actor-talks-about-becoming-the-main-character-lenny-scene-more/ |title=Red Dead Redemption 2 Interview: The Actor Behind Arthur Morgan Talks About Becoming the Main Character, Lenny Scene & More |last=Madsen |first=Hayes |publisher=Twinfinite |date=February 19, 2019 |accessdate=May 12, 2019 |archiveurl=http://www.webcitation.org/78It5tYdp |archivedate=May 11, 2019 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Variety\">{{cite web |url=https://variety.com/2018/gaming/features/red-dead-redemption-2-narrative-interview-1202992401/ |title=The Story Behind the Story of 'Red Dead Redemption 2' |last=Crecente |first=Brian |work=[[Variety (magazine)|Variety]] |publisher=[[Penske Media Corporation]] |date=October 24, 2018 |accessdate=May 8, 2019 |archiveurl=http://www.webcitation.org/78DBbVpsB |archivedate=May 8, 2019 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"VentureBeat\">{{cite web |url=https://venturebeat.com/2018/12/05/red-dead-redemption-a-deep-dive-into-rockstars-game-design/view-all/ |title=Red Dead Redemption 2: A deep dive into Rockstar's game design |last=Takahashi |first=Dean |publisher=[[VentureBeat]] |date=December 5, 2018 |accessdate=May 11, 2019 |archiveurl=http://www.webcitation.org/78HlDucxs |archivedat